    {
      "parameters": {
        "content": "# Deliver a weekly summary with Notion and Telegram on autopilot\n\n**Pattern:** Scheduled Digest · **Level:** Advanced · **Trigger:** Scheduled\n\n## What it does\nDeliver a weekly summary with Notion and Telegram on autopilot. It runs automatically on a schedule.\n\n## Why it exists\nManual inbox triage is slow and error-prone; this workflow makes the process repeatable, monitored and hands-off, with failures surfaced instead of silently lost.\n\n## Main flow\nDaily Schedule → Read Recent from Notion → Newest First → Trim to Digest Size → Summarize Content (AI) → Render as HTML → Post Digest to Telegram → …\n\n## Use it for\n- Teams that want to scheduled digest without manual effort\n- Anyone automating inbox triage in marketing\n- Replacing a fragile manual process with a reliable workflow\n\n## You get\n- Scales without extra headcount\n- Removes copy-paste errors\n- Saves hours of manual work each week\n\n## Before first run\nConnect credentials: Anthropic API key; Notion integration token; Slack OAuth2; Telegram bot token.\nFollow the color key: 🟦 entry · 🟪 AI · 🟫 actions · ⬜ utilities · 🟩 outputs · 🟥 error rail.\nEach node has its own doc card underneath — read those before editing.",
        "width": 480,
        "height": 900
      },
      "type": "n8n-nodes-base.stickyNote",
      "typeVersion": 1,
      "position": [
        -830,
        80
      ],
      "id": "2b4dd93d-17ac-12ff-243b-64f3260c55d1",
      "name": "📘 Workflow Overview"
    },
